<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_2"/>Left <persName>Mangala</persName>'s and came through
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_3"/>a great many villages all deserted at
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_4"/>our approach in consequence of the 
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_5"/>vengeance taken by <persName>Dugumbe</persName><choice><sic>s</sic><corr>'s</corr></choice> party
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_6"/>for the murder of some of his <figure facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_fig1" n="1"><figDesc>Livingstone has drawn the head of an African individual here.</figDesc></figure>
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_7"/>followers = <persName>Kasongo</persName>'s men
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_8"/>eager plunderers of other <term type="tribe">Manyema</term>
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_9"/>had to scold and threaten <del type="strikethrough">them</del>
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_10"/>and will set some to watch their
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_11"/>deeds tomorrow = Plantains <figure facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_fig2" n="2"><figDesc>Livingstone has drawn the head of an African individual here.</figDesc></figure>
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_12"/>very abundant and good =
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_13"/>came to <placeName><region>Kitette</region></placeName> and lodged in a 
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_14"/>village of <term type="tribe">Loembo</term> = about thirty
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_15"/>smith<del>y</del><add place="inline">ies</add> or rather foundr<del type="cancelled">d</del>ies in <figure facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_fig3" n="3"><figDesc>Livingstone has drawn the head of an African individual here.</figDesc></figure> the
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_16"/>villages we passed = they are
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_17"/>very high in the roof to avoid fires
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_18"/>and <figure facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_fig4" n="4"><figDesc>Livingstone has drawn an African hut here</figDesc></figure> thatched with a sort of wild
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_19"/><w>plan-<space dim="horizontal" extent="4" unit="chars"/>tain</w> leaf from which sparks
<lb facs="#zliv_000095_0022_CLX_20"/>and<space dim="horizontal" extent="5" unit="chars"/>rain run off equally well -</p>
